den Arbeit lautet, welche Rolle die Entscheidungsträger der Finanzaufsicht zukünftig spielen sollen, um eine solche Krise wie die aktuelle Finanzkrise zu vermeiden und - für den Fall, dass ihre Verhinderung scheitert - ihre Auswirkungen zu verringern. Vor diesem Hintergrund geht es hier um die Rolle einer supranationalen Finanzaufsicht in einem regional integrierten Finanzsystem.  aThis work seeks to describe the role that actors in charge of financial system oversight should play in the future to prevent a crisis similar to the current financial crisis and – should prevention fail – to mitigate its effects. Against this backdrop, the work examines the role of supranational financial supervision as part of a regionally integrated financial system.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aFinanzmärkte. 7aLAW / Commercial / General.2bisacsh  aFinancial Markets.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Law - 2000 - 2014z9783110636208oZDB-23-GLA08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2012z9783110288995oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET RECHTSWISSENSCHAFTEN 2012z9783110288919oZDB-23-DGC0 cprintz978311028813140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311028819340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110288193423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110288193/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGCb2012  aZDB-23-DGGb2012  aZDB-23-GLAc2000d2014